.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申鳩up,咩都唔識"},{"pid":"671d5f4e563b75ad660b6a6efd8b769ff1476826","tid":151011,"uid":41695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"個記者把聲好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44830d5bc25119a9491cebb9f09232a4ffbd651","tid":151011,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2485f77c824d044c798b8bce2baaf96c862cfe9","tid":151011,"uid":29189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一塞車真係隨時奶閪，但就咁車場又係奶閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登仔你地係司機會點做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吹熄</blockquote><br />\n你當on9的 連登仔當然第一時間走喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你錯 連登仔用口一吹就熄曬"},{"pid":"2159c02737d61ced3c86ea0e34f6d3a844cde20f","tid":151011,"uid":12443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9<br />\n停車場有消防花灑頭架ma<br />\n拎碌棍整爛佢等水灑落去仲快啦<br />\n垃圾司機以為自己好撚醒<br />\n一出馬路塞埋車果陣睇你點走</blockquote><br />\n你去揸囉，講你就巴撚閉，做你咪又係成條柒咁企係度瀨晒屎</blockquote><br />\n你up乜9呀傻西<br />\n宜家叫佢唔好揸出去呀<br />\n唔塞車只係佢好彩咋</blockquote><br />\n而家串9梗你呀，你吹撚脹呀廢9</blockquote><br />\n結果就係無塞，結果就係救熄左，理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4c97d5afa05676ece5d403311143c4d7002793","tid":151011,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"連登有無咁多on9呀, ok都接一餐"},{"pid":"9784c170de0ffa9111b6b904e9813355a7cf814b","tid":151011,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"理得佢塞唔塞 駛左出停車場先算"},{"pid":"eeae16b824b25870f6c2a3318283dddb2e1829c9","tid":151011,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大廈保安都係仆街黎</blockquote><br />\n不過咁，如果叫消防車黎嘅話起碼要用多幾倍時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n著火呀大佬<br />\n<br />\n著緊火仲叫人駛走佢.同叫人跳樓,跳還跳咪係我地方跳有乜分別?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n著緊火緊係叫人安全地走人先啦</blockquote><br />\n你覺得停車場+工厦蔓延火勢唔大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n衝出馬路到，咁岩塞車又爆炸，真係GTA"},{"pid":"ca5dc312411dcc3734cb7f3948ce9356fe9ce2a8","tid":151011,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:33:55.000Z","msg":"連登仔無受過專業訓練，所以一定會即刻走，以免越幫越忙"},{"pid":"746e566329bb2ea4a74780be4147b8d98a09012d","tid":151011,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一塞車真係隨時奶閪，但就咁車場又係奶閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登仔你地係司機會點做？</blockquote><br />\n即刻上黎開post問<br />\n<br />\n而家揸緊架烈火垃圾車<br />\n去邊到好"},{"pid":"1adad921f303709ed0839ee7ea50a4beb0e481aa","tid":151011,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一塞車真係隨時奶閪，但就咁車場又係奶閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登仔你地係司機會點做？</blockquote><br />\n即刻上黎開post問<br />\n<br />\n而家揸緊架烈火垃圾車<br />\n去邊到好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal